column5: Hey guys just wondering if anyone knows how the ice is on quinte planning on making the drive up soon
Check Quinte fishing board.  I haven't been down, but it seems that it might be shaping up for the weekend.  Take that with a grain of salt, conditions change very quickly down there!
John Whyte posted up a nice report from earlier this week on his lake simcoe message board.   Definitely some spots to fish thre this weekend
